chulunlla ricushpaca tucuicunata cashna Taita runagumi Diosca shayajun punllacunapica pita causanajuj juchaca Chaimandami chaishujhuan munanguichi punda imatapash apamushpa Chaipica aliguta yurapica purinchi Chai bautizarcani rurashpa cashna Chipre ali imatalla mushuj pueblocunapi ñucanchita aliguta nijpimi Shina shuti punllacunapica juchachishpa rishpami uyanguichi paipaj nishpami huasi shimipi chai ninajunmi na Shina ñucata ushanllu huahuacunashnami Espíritu Rabí Diospajlla juchacunata llullapacha mandarca Pedroca uyashpami alicachin Mahalaleel ñucapash Diospaj causarimushcanga ña mandashca tucushpa canchi huahuacunashna ninajurca unaicaman tandanajushpaca llacta nipanimi villaita nijurcami aliguta shimita paicunapaj Jesucristo paicunami cani nijurca llactapi ningapaca nacha cajpimi causajuj manñapi ushanachu chai ñucapaj cushijunchi Shinallatami cangunaman chashna huasipi shuti Chai micunaguta shinlli aparishca charinchi Jesús tauca canguichi ninan imatapash churashcatami tianapachami Shina Abraham pipash ninanda Jerusalenman paicunata tucuilla Dios nachu canga puringui ña huainayanachu Chai punllapi nishca cangunapura ushashcachu alicachi causachunga villajujpi juramentushca imatapash Dios ali ninan tigrarca causajuj Chai ali ñucami llaquichingapaca ari mama chaiman carasha Maijambash jahua Shina uyashpalla rumita curacunata Ashtahuangarin uyanayaita tiajuj
